description.excerpt: * Instead of cropping out a portion from the decoder part and concatening it in encoder part, the whole portion is so calculated to ensure the feature maps are not cropped out, rather concatenated wholly. The input image size had been adjusted accordingly. This should decrease potential loss of info due to cropping.
Nuclei segmentaion using UNET and some experiments
